{"tid":2414354,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"18歲男生連中5彈被捕 藏雷射筆罪成判更生中心 母庭上痛哭","createTime":"2021-02-19T10:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T13:56:12.000Z","uid":56115,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1d4deb404348fb11767df0fb845d0703154c04","tid":2414354,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:37:05.000Z","msg":"網民前年10月在尖沙嘴發起追究警暴遊行，最終演變成警民衝突。警方晚上在旺角施放催淚彈驅散人群，其間有男學生被指管有行山杖，背部連中5發胡椒彈後被捕，及後在警署內被指背囊藏有雷射筆，早前被裁定在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器罪名成立。裁判官梁嘉琪今判刑時指，為收阻嚇之效及反映嚴重性，選擇聽取感化官的建議，判男生進入更生中心。患有思覺失調的被告母親離庭時掩面痛哭，需由親友攙扶。<br />\n<br />\n梁官早前裁定被告管有雷射筆，再加上被告裝束，被告實可預期有衝突發生。而涉案雷射筆屬「3B」級及寫有「Danger」警告字眼，<span class=\"red\">梁官不接納辯方指雷射筆僅用於煩擾警員的說法</span>，認為唯一合理推論是用於傷人，裁定被告罪名成立。"},{"pid":"54416afa89daa69d71892f35566f25fbacfaecd6","tid":2414354,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:37:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/VLEUOZG23NBMTB7LDW2MYD5MCY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FVLEUOZG23NBMTB7LDW2MYD5MCY%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGt6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=0be5227d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210219%2FVLEUOZG23NBMTB7LDW2MYD5MCY%2F&h=6fec2136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210219/VLEUOZG23NBMTB7LDW2MYD5MCY/</a>"},{"pid":"56fccf6e793eeb1a7e9aaca8b599c0f0207bcb23","tid":2414354,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba38728d65f8d945d92684b07bf63251e1730d89","tid":2414354,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c2a8682f9a828d955e7fbbf49610a401beb2e77","tid":2414354,"uid":184261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-0